strings: <voice_0x010012E8><se_low>Conduct illegal business: If you go north from the mountain foot, you will reach Orkutsk. Be careful when you travel.
<voice_0x010012EA><se_low>King of tricks: How's Amy doing? Is she cold at night?
<voice_0x010012EB><se_low>Conduct illegal business: Sorry, I need your help.
<voice_0x010012EC><se_low>Conduct illegal business: If you know Marek on Orkok, give him a pass.
I will accept a Maltese suitcase.
<voice_0x010012ED><se_low>Conduct illegal business: I want you to give him the bag because he knows how to use herbs like me. thanks
<voice_0x010012EE><se_low>King of tricks: Then go to Orkutsk!
